\v 3 Ingakunyengetedza kakawanda here? Inotaura zvakanyorova kwauri here?
\v 4 Ingaita sungano newe here\x + 31.1.\x*? Uchaitora ive muranda rinhi narinhi here\x + 3.19.\x*?
\v 5 Ungatamba nayo seshiri here? Kana ungaisungira vanasikana vako here\x + Map. 104.26.\x*?
\v 6 Vatengi\x + Ruk. 5.7,10.\x* vangatengeserana nayo here\x + 2 Madz. 6.23.\x*? Vangaigoverana here\x + Gen.. 33.1. Vato. 7.16.\x* pakati pevatengesi\x + Zvir. 31.24. Isa. 23.11. Hos. 12.7. Zef. 1.11. Vato. 1.31,32.\x*?
\v 7 Ungazadza ganda rayo nemiseve ine nzeve here, kana musoro wayo nepfumo rehove?
\v 8 Isa pairi ruoko rwako; rangarira hondo; usapamhidza.
\v 9 Tarira, tariro yake ichava manyepo\x + Zvir. 30.6.\x*. Naiyo ichakandirwa\x + 20.4.\x* pasi here pakuiona\x + Map. 37.24. Jer. 22.28.\x*?
\v 10 Hakuna anotyisa kuti angaimutsa. Zvino ndiani angazvimisa pamberi pangu\x + 30.21.\x*?
\v 11 Ndiani\x + 35.7. VaRom. 11.35.\x* angauya pamberi pangu kuti ndiripe\x + 3.12. 30.27. Mat. 17.25.\x*? Chiri pasi pematenga ese ndechangu\x + Eki. 19.5.\x*.
