\v 12 Handinganyarari pamusoro pemitezo yayo, kana nyaya yesimba \add rayo\add*, kana kunaka kwechimiro chayo\x + 18.13.\x*.
\v 13 Ndiani angaratidza chiso chenguvo yayo? Ndiani angauya nematomu ake akapetwa kaviri\x + Isa. 25.7.\x*?
\v 14 Ndiani angazarura masuwo echiso chayo? Mazino ayo anotyisa mativi ese\x + 39.20.\x*.
\v 15 Makwande ayo ane kuzvikudza, akavharirwa nemucherechedzo wakasimbiswa.
\v 16 Rimwe riri pedo nerimwe, kuti pasava nemhepo inopinda pakati pawo.
\v 17 Akabatana anonamatirana\x + 41.23. 38.38.\x* kuti asaparadzaniswa\x + 38.30.\x*.
\v 18 Kuhotsira kwayo kunopenya chiedza\x + 31.26.\x*; uye meso ayo akaita sezvifunhiro zvemeso zvemangwanani\x + 3.9.\x*.
\v 19 Mumuromo mayo munobuda mazhenje; ubaribari hwemoto hunosvatika.
\v 20 Mumhino dzayo munobuda utsi, sehari inopfungaira\x + 20.26.\x* nenhokwe\x + 41.2.\x*.
\v 21 Mweya wayo unopfutidza mazimbe, uye murazvo unobuda mumuromo mayo\x + 2 Sam. 22.13.\x*.
\v 22 Mumutsipa mayo munogara simba, uye mberi kwayo kunopembera kusuruvara.
\v 23 Nhindi dzenyama yayo dzakabatana, dzakasimba pairi, hadzizununguswi\x + 41.23. 38.38.\x*.
